    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Header Reference Schema</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-4">Populate downstream operational request executions using standard key headers:</p>
    
    <pre><code class="language-bash">curl -X POST https://api.yourdomain.com/api/chat \
  -H "X-API-Key: your-api-key-here" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "Hello!"}]
  }'</code></pre>

